original_title: Rabbit Ears - Jack and the Beanstalk
overview: When Jack sells his cow for some lousy looking beans, his mother goes into a rage and throws the beans out the window. However, Jack soon discovers that those beans were no ordinary beans and he begins a journey to get the riches that lies on top of the beanstalk. However, Jack soon discovers that the riches are not the only things on the beanstalk.
title: Rabbit Ears - Jack and the Beanstalk
